; Coverage test for filters.cc lines 840-841, 845
; Test revalued filter with market values.
; The revalued filter creates temporary posts with the revalued total,
; exercising the as_amount path in handle_value.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/15 AAPL $160.00

2024/01/01 Buy stock
    Assets:Investment    10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash         $-1500.00

test reg Assets:Investment --market --gain
24-Jan-15 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $100.00      $100.00
end test
